entries.femaleVariant: You don't smell it? The air...! Pfff, mmm,don't even need filters! Not like in Santo Domingo.
Yeah, 'stead you catch a bullet for no reason. Least in SanDomo they tell ya why first.
Aw, you're just jealous. If you just got up a little earlier, worked a little harder...
Finally! My whole life, always wanted to live here.
Where, the Glen? Downtown I get, but the Glen?!
What if you just let me live my fuckin' life?
Sure, sure. Anyway, let's get a drink. No worries, my treat.
